	<td>
		<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="3" color="#9f3215"><b>    An Old Silver Coin</b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="#9f3215">
			<b><a href="mailto:chshrcat@hotmail.com">Skeezix</a> | 
                        12/30/1999 4:35:23 AM</b></font></p>
			
			<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">I found a new item in Grobb on the Rathe server which <BR>
is apparently part of a quest (the GM would not confirm <BR>
it either way, and I don't think the item was around <BR>
before the last patch). It is &quot;An Old Silver Coin&quot;, and it<BR>
is magic/lore/no drop, all/all, weight 0.1 with no visible<BR>
properties or effects; interestingly, it respawned within <BR>
five minutes of my picking it up. I found it in the pool <BR>
immediately in front of the bar. I have hailed most of <BR>
the NPCs in both Grobb and Innothule Swamp, and have<BR>
yet to find where the quest starts. Let the search begin!
	<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
			</p>
	</td>
